Package ss.pentago.network.protocol

Enum ProtocolCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ProtocolCode>
      • ss.pentago.network.protocol.ProtocolCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ProtocolCode>
    public enum ProtocolCode
extends java.lang.Enum<ProtocolCode>
    An Enum to store all possible (supported) client-server protocol codes. This is meant to simplify checking and to standardize communication handling.
